{"title_page": "Arko Pravo Mukherjee", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian singer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name                 = Arko Pravo Mukherjee\n| image                = Arko2.jpg\n| caption              = Arko Pravo Mukherjee\n| birth_name           = Arko Pravo Mukherjee\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1983|005|19}}\n| birth_place          = [[Kolkata]], West Bengal, India\n| yearsactive          = 2012\u2013present\n| occupation           = {{hlist|Music composer|singer-songwriter}}\n| genre                = Bengali modern\n| website              = http://www.arkoworld.com/\n| background           = solo_singer\n}}\nDr. Arko Pravo Mukherjee is an Indian [[singer-songwriter]] working in the Bollywood film industry since 2012. ''[[Jism 2]]'' was his debut film as a music composer and lyricist.<ref>{{cite news |date=1 August 2012 |title= 'Jism 2' songs are not copied, says composer |url=http://www.ibnlive.com/news/india/jism-2-songs-are-not-copied-says-composer-493266.html |work=IBN Live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=17 April 2012 |title= Arko to compose music for 'Jism 2' |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/music/news-and-interviews/Arko-to-compose-music-for-Jism-2/articleshow/12700322.cms?referral=PM |work=The Times of India}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=28 April 2012 |title= New Prescription Arko Pravo Mukherjee to compose music for Jism 2 |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/arko-pravo-mukherjee-to-compose-music-for-jism-2/1/186437.html |work=India Today}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=1 December 2014 |title= A quick four with Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/141201/entertainment-tvmusic/article/quick-four-arko-pravo-mukherjee |work=Deccan Chronicle}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=7 November 2014 |title= Arko Pravo Mukherjee sings an EDM number |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/arko-pravo-mukherjee-sings-an-edm-number/ |work=The Indian Express}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=10 February 2015 |title= Tips Music signs Arko Pravo Mukherjee for ten songs of their upcoming films |url=http://www.radioandmusic.com/biz/music/artiste/tips-music-signs-arko-pravo-mukherjee-ten-songs-their-upcoming-films-150210 |work=Radio And Music}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=13 February 2015 |title= On a high note: Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/on-a-high-note-arko-pravo-mukherjee/ |work=The Indian Express}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=8 August 2012 |title= Item songs don't work anymore: Dr Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/news/Item-songs-dont-work-anymore-Dr-Arko-Pravo-Mukherjee/articleshow/15400604.cms |work=The Times of India}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=7 February 2015 |title=Signing A Deal |url=http://www.boxofficeindia.co.in/signing-a-deal/ |publisher=Box Office India |access-date=12 December 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222074025/http://www.boxofficeindia.co.in/signing-a-deal/ |archive-date=22 December 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=28 November 2014 |title= Nothing works beyond Bollywood, says 'Aaj Phir Tum Pe' singer Arko |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/music/nothing-works-beyond-bollywood-says-aaj-phir-tum-pe-singer-arko/story-oT7jLq630CZqKAWDG8AELI.html |work=Hindustan Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=29 December 2014 |title= 2014 Rewind: Bollywood musicians pick their favourite songs of the year |url=http://www.mid-day.com/articles/2014-rewind-bollywood-musicians-pick-their-favourite-songs-of-the-year/15873179 |work=MidDay}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=14 July 2012 |title= Music Review: 'Jism 2' has wonderful tracks |url=http://www.ibnlive.com/news/music/music-review-jism-2-has-wonderful-tracks-487734.html |work=IBN Live}}</ref>He is also known for singing several Bengali and Nepali music. According to Industry Experts and Bollywood Media Reviews, Arko is among the most promising new sensations in Indian Music and is also among the busiest Music Directors of Bollywood.<ref>https://m.imdb.com/name/nm3334275/bio?ref_=m_mn_ov_bio</ref><ref>https://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/bengali/music/arko-pravo-mukherjee-is-a-married-man/amp_articleshow/66360261.cmsp</ref><ref>https://m.republicworld.com/entertainment-news/bollywood-news/kriti-sanons-bareilly-ki-barfi-movie-songs.html</ref><ref>https://scroll.in/reel/804588/composer-arko-mukherjee-raises-the-pitch-with-kapoor-sons</ref>\n\n==Early life==\nArko Pravo Mukherjee was born on 19 May 1983 to Dr. Apurba Kumar Mukherjee and Mahasweta Mukherjee in [[Kolkata]], West Bengal. He attended school at [[Don Bosco School, Park Circus]], Kolkata. Arko graduated with MBBS in 2007 from [[Burdwan Medical College]]. He completed his internship at [[Calcutta Medical College]] and then in 2008 he shifted to Mumbai to pursue a career in Bollywood film industry as a music director, singer songwriter.<ref>{{cite news |date=4 October 2015 |title= MEET DR DO MORE OF MUSIC |url=http://www.dailypioneer.com/sunday-edition/sunday-pioneer/backpack/meet-dr-do-more-of-music.html |work=Daily Pioneer}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=9 December 2014 |title=Rising Arko Pravo sets solid foot in Bollywood |url=http://archive.asianage.com/people/rising-arko-pravo-sets-solid-foot-bollywood-547 |work=The Asian Age |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222170522/http://archive.asianage.com/people/rising-arko-pravo-sets-solid-foot-bollywood-547 |archivedate=22 December 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=2 December 2014 |title=A quick four with Arko Pravo |url=http://archive.asianage.com/music/quick-four-arko-pravo-147 |work=The Asian Age |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222170445/http://archive.asianage.com/music/quick-four-arko-pravo-147 |archivedate=22 December 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2 November 2015 |title= Melody matters |url=http://www.asianage.com/music/melody-matters-504 |work=The Asian Age}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Hindi filmography===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"| \n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n|'''Year'''\n|'''Film Name/Album'''\n|'''Song'''\n|'''Singer(s)'''\n|'''Notes''' \n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2012 ||rowspan=4|''[[Jism 2]]''<ref>{{cite news |date=14 July 2012 |title= Made in Calcutta: A DBPC boy has scored the soundtrack. Meet Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1120714/jsp/entertainment/story_15725199.jsp |work=The Telegraph}}</ref>  || Abhi Abhi (Male) || [[KK (singer)|KK]] ||\n|-\n|| Yeh Jism Hai Toh Kya<ref>{{cite news |date=3 August 2012 |title= \"Yeh Jism' is very close to my heart\" \u2013 Dr.Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/3778/ |work=Bollywood Hungama}}</ref> ||rowspan=\"2\"|[[Ali Azmat]]\n|\n|-\n|| Maula\n|\n|-\n|| Abhi Abhi (Duet) || KK, [[Akriti Kakar]], [[Shreya Ghoshal]]\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|2014 || rowspan=2|''[[Yaariyan (2014 film)|Yaariyan]]''<ref>{{cite news |date=27 December 2013 |title= I don't mind being part of a multi- composer movie: Arko Pravo Mukherjee |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/news/Arko-Pravo-Mukherjee-takes-us-through-his-eventful-journey-in-Bollywood/articleshow/27976957.cms? |work=The Times of India}}</ref> || Allah Waariyan || [[Shafqat Amanat Ali]] \n|\n|-\n|| Zor Lagaake Haisha || [[Vishal Dadlani]] \n|\n|-\n|| ''[[Hate Story 2]]'' || Aaj Phir Tumpe Pyaar Aaya Hai || [[Arijit Singh]], [[Samira Koppikar]]\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Tamanchey]]'' || Dildara || [[Sonu Nigam]] ||\n|-\n||Dildara (Reprise) || Arko\n|\n|-\n|| ''[[The Shaukeens]]''<ref>{{cite news |date=23 October 2014 |title= The Shaukeens : On a Song \u2013 What started in the studio ended at a party |url=http://times